title: Cuisinart 11-piece Chef's Classic Stainless Steel Cookware Set (77-11G) Demo Video
description:
Learn more: http://www.cuisinart.com/products/cookware/chefs_classic_stainless/sets_ccs/77-11g.html

The kitchens of France were the inspiration behind the elegant Cuisinart® Chef's Classic™ Stainless Cookware Collection. The gem of any kitchen, this 11-piece set features stainless steel and pure aluminum encapsulated at the base to ensure fast and even heating. Put style back into cooking with this beautiful cookware set.
